OL,3,CMan framed by corrupt police officer
OL,4,Cfor stealing has name cleared
OL,6,FA man who was jailed after being
OL,7,Fframed by a corrupt police officer's
OL,8,Fevidence has had his name cleared
OL,9,Fposthumously at the Court of Appeal.
OL,11,FErrol Campbell, who died in 2004, had
OL,12,Fhis conviction for theft and
OL,13,Fconspiracy to steal from a goods depot
OL,14,Fin South London quashed at the London
OL,15,Fcourt today.
