OL,3,CMan framed by corrupt police officer
OL,4,Cfor stealing has name cleared
OL,6,FHe was found guilty in April 1977 and
OL,7,Fsentenced to a total of 18 months' in
OL,8,Fprison, at the Old Bailey, following
OL,9,Fthefts from the Bricklayers Arms Goods
OL,10,FDepot, where he was a British Rail
OL,11,Femployee.
OL,13,FThe case against him was led by the
OL,14,Fdiscredited British Transport Police
OL,15,Fofficer DS Derek Ridgewell.
