OL,3,CMan framed by corrupt police officer
OL,4,Cfor stealing has name cleared
OL,6,FGiving his judgment on Thursday, Lord
OL,7,FJustice Holroyde, sitting with Mr
OL,8,FJustice Butcher and Mr Justice Wall,
OL,9,Fsaid that it was with "regret" that
OL,10,Fthe court could not undo Mr Campbell's
OL,11,Fsuffering.
OL,13,FHe added: "We can however, and do,
OL,14,Fallow the appeal brought on his
OL,15,Fbehalf, and quash his conviction.
OL,17,F"We hope that will at least bring some
OL,18,Fcomfort to Mr Campbell's family who
OL,19,Fsurvive."
