OL,4,Cfor stealing has name cleared
OL,6,FDS Ridgewell led the case against Mr
OL,7,FCampbell and several others, but along
OL,8,Fwith colleagues DC Douglas Ellis and
OL,9,FDC Alan Keeling, later admitted
OL,10,Fstealing from the same goods depot.
OL,12,FMr Campbell unsuccessfully appealed
OL,13,Fhis conviction in 1978.
OL,15,FHis son submitted an application
OL,16,FCriminal Cases Review Commission
OL,17,F(CCRC) in September 2024, with the
OL,18,Fhelp of the charity APPEAL.
