OL,3,CMan framed by corrupt police officer
OL,4,Cfor stealing has name cleared
OL,6,FFollowing a review, the CCRC found
OL,7,Fthere was a real possibility that,
OL,8,Flike the convictions of 11 other
OL,9,Fpeople that have been referred to the
OL,10,Fcourt, Mr Campbell's conviction would
OL,11,Fbe quashed, and it referred the
OL,12,Fconviction in February 2025.
OL,14,F'The conviction caused absolute misery
OL,15,Fto my dad and our family,' Errol
OL,16,FCampbell's son speaks out after his
OL,17,Fconviction
