OL,3,CMan framed by corrupt police officer
OL,4,Cfor stealing has name cleared
OL,6,FIn a statement read out by his
OL,7,Fsolicitor, Matt Foot, Errol Campbell
OL,8,FJr, the son of Errol Campbell, said:
OL,9,F"The British Transport Police knew
OL,10,Fthat Detective Sergeant Derek
OL,11,FRidgewell was corrupt, and they let
OL,12,Fhim carry on regardless with what he
OL,13,Fwas doing.
OL,15,F"My dad always said he was innocent,
OL,16,Fand today, that's finally been
OL,17,Fconfirmed, almost 50 years later.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
