OL,3,CMan framed by corrupt police officer
OL,4,Cfor stealing has name cleared
OL,6,F"I'm angry that Ridgewell is not alive
OL,7,Ffor this day and that he never went to
OL,8,Fprison for all the people he fitted
OL,9,Fup. He never answered for his crimes.
OL,11,F"He was a great family man and looked
OL,12,Fafter us as children, and he was
OL,13,Fdapper. He was a good man."
OL,15,FIn August 2023 the CCRC referred the
OL,16,Fconvictions of Mr Campbell's co-
OL,17,Fdefendants, Saliah Mehmet and Basil
OL,18,FPeterkin, after it tracked down their
OL,19,Ffamily members.
