OL,6,FThe convictions were both quashed in
OL,7,FJanuary 2024.
OL,9,FIn 1980, Ridgewell, Ellis and Keeling
OL,10,Fpleaded guilty to conspiracy to steal
OL,11,Ffrom the Bricklayers' Arms Depot.
OL,13,FRidgewell died in prison before he had
OL,14,Fcompleted his sentence.
