OL,7,Ffound that their criminal activities
OL,8,Fbetween January 1977 and April 1978
OL,9,Fresulted in the loss from the depot of
OL,10,Fgoods to the value of about #364,000
OL,11,F"an enormous sum of money at that
OL,12,Ftime".
